   \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/a-smartphone-linking-to-various-smart-home-device-icons-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/a-smartphone-linking-to-various-smart-home-device-icons-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/a-smartphone-linking-to-various-smart-home-device-icons-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/a-smartphone-linking-to-various-smart-home-device-icons-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"a smartphone linking to various smart home device icons\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/a-smartphone-linking-to-various-smart-home-device-icons-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/a-smartphone-linking-to-various-smart-home-device-icons-1.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/how-secure-home-smart-devices/\" title=\"How I Secure the Smart Devices in My Home\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tHow I Secure the Smart Devices in My Home\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eYour smart home devices make life easier, but don\u0026#39;t forget to secure them against hackers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"factory-reset-your-device\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Factory Reset Your Device\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA factory reset removes sensitive information stored in the device like Wi-Fi passwords, username and account passwords, credit card details, addresses, and other types of data that can be used for identity theft, financial fraud, and cyberattacks.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFor instance, some contain data like the pre-shared key (PSK) that can give threat actors access to your home network. Other sensitive and personal information, including photos or medical records, can also be used to blackmail you.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_13\"\u003e\n\n        \n            \u003cp\u003eFor some devices, a factory reset or hard reset involves just pushing a button on the device for a few seconds; others would require you to do this using the device’s dedicated app. Check the user manual and follow the steps carefully to ensure you do this successfully.\u003c/p\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"follow-local-electronic-waste-disposal-guidelines\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e4 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Follow Local Electronic Waste Disposal Guidelines\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/why-e-waste-is-dangerous/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eElectronic wastes are more dangerous than you think\u003c/a\u003e. When electronics are simply tossed in the trash, they end up in landfills where they release toxic substances like lead and mercury that can seep deep into the soil and groundwater. This is why local governments have electronic waste disposal guidelines that meet international standards.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSome cities collect unwanted electronics for free to ensure that they don’t end up in landfills. Residents are just required to bring the devices to a drop-off location. However, cities can\u0026#39;t ensure the complete destruction of data in the device, so you\u0026#39;re advised to sanitize them before you drop them off.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIf you\u0026#39;re going to dispose of smart home devices in bulk, especially those that contain other people’s data, you ask vendors for a certificate of data destruction. This assures clients that the data in the devices has been permanently destroyed according to local privacy laws and regulations.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAs we regularly upgrade and replace our devices, electronic waste disposal has become a regular task. Unlike most other waste, however, devices contain harmful substances that can poison the environment—on top of a wealth of sensitive data that puts you at risk of cyberattacks and fraud if these land in the wrong hands. So, it’s important to follow these guidelines to mitigate the risks.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
